<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880617-0174 </DOCNO><HL> Medical Graphics Gets Order </HL><SO> </SO><CO> MGCC </CO><DATELINE> ST. PAUL, Minn.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Medical Graphics Corp. said it received a contract from a major Minnesota hospital for the purchase of 16 systems used for diagnosis and treatment of lung disease. Terms weren't disclosed.    The company said the 16 systems, which will be shipped throughout the year, represent the largest single order in the company's history. </TEXT></DOC>